      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride that's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s been well-loved, super reliable, and honestly still looks great on the road. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or those fun weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and it's totally ready for its next owner to hit the road. Come take it for a spin!",
