    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example is a driver\u2019s specification, boasting a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system to ensure optimal valve timing and torque delivery. The chassis retains its tactile precision through a factory Variable M Differential Lock and updated bushings. While the exterior displays minor patina consistent with its mileage, the performance envelope remains sharp, with a linear power band and a communicative suspension setup that rewards technical driving. All major mechanical hurdles common to this platform have been proactively addressed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
