      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a superior blend of performance and reliability. This unit has been subjected to a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our stringent criteria for mechanical excellence and roadworthiness. Boasting a refined interior and a robust powertrain, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the executive buyer who prioritizes long-term value and proven dependability. Experience the assurance of a vehicle that has been curated for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
