    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving engine breathes through individual throttle bodies and utilizes double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul, ensuring structural and mechanical integrity. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings, and the cooling system has been refreshed to handle spirited driving. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain dialed-in for the purist driver.",
